{"tid":1340651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[識法律入]香港有冇私人檢控嘅法律","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:16:56.000Z","uid":201662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7e5e9a2f5c2670091207f502ccea6b37b6b35c44","tid":1340651,"uid":201662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:08:12.000Z","msg":"係人都知，係正常情況下，係狗仔搵證據，之後交比律政去告<br />\n<br />\n但狗仔如果唔搵證據，咁普通市民可唔可以自行搵證據，再去告一個人，而且係刑事檢控，要對方坐返幾年咁<br />\n<br />\n見到班牛屎佬有黑警撐腰就可以濫用私刑，唔通普通市民真係冇告對方嘅權利？否則，即使有獨立調查委員會，都只係告到班濫權黑警，班廢老同牛屎佬都只會一直逍遙法外"},{"pid":"b625d043d869aca3cb2be423c3885e37ee3461ef","tid":1340651,"uid":201662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:12:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a833a7ec5605803c7ea1dd29e4ffa1128c05d57","tid":1340651,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:13:34.000Z","msg":"公民拘捕權"},{"pid":"fa1226d91f05b798bd80a03aa90fdf8f04bdf926","tid":1340651,"uid":201662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a833a7ec5605803c7ea1dd29e4ffa1128c05d57","tid":1340651,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:13:34.000Z","msg":"公民拘捕權"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"拉完係交比黑警，咁之後都係交比黑警做嘢，唔通我地都可以用個人名義去告佢？"},{"pid":"1a53450ef93de3419afcd1fa134030b79ef574a6","tid":1340651,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa1226d91f05b798bd80a03aa90fdf8f04bdf926","tid":1340651,"uid":201662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a833a7ec5605803c7ea1dd29e4ffa1128c05d57","tid":1340651,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:13:34.000Z","msg":"公民拘捕權"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"拉完係交比黑警，咁之後都係交比黑警做嘢，唔通我地都可以用個人名義去告佢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:16:56.000Z","msg":"c鳥"}]}